{"id": "zfr1695290811319", "title": "colorbox", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "colorbox"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zfr1695290811319.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">colorbox</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: clrmess \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: clrmess \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ylq1665702607548.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: commit \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: commit \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpl1665702560927.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/zfr1695290811319.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/zfr1695290811319.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/zfr1695290811319.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_4814677\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_4814677\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zfr1695290811319.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zfr1695290811319.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zfr1695290811319.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gix1665702628957\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"gix1665702628957__colorbox_212017\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Start the Microsoft Windows Color dialog box. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gix1665702628957__topic_d70190e1_d70191e1_d70192e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104zfr1695290811319_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"gix1665702628957__codeblock_c4c_swz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">colorbox {/hex | /rgb}  {/full}   {\"Color\"}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"gix1665702628957__section_w1436ab1b7b5_w1437ab1b7_w1438ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gix1665702628957__p_d70196e1_d70197e1_d70198e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">colorbox /hex /full \"#00FF00\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"gix1665702628957__note_uwz_ncb_wyb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">colorbox</code> widget supports accessibility\n            feature only for testing purposes and screen readers only. For more information, see\n               <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"abr1688541158363.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/abr1688541158363.html\" title=\"Uniface exposes the UI of generated Windows desktop applications to screen readers and automation tools for a number of widgets. By exposing the underlying infrastructure, screen readers and automated testing tools can target supported UI elements, and retrieve information regarding their name, value, and status. For these purposes, a mixture of two different technologies has been used - UI Automation and MSAA (Microsoft Active Accessibility).\">Accessibility</a>.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gix1665702628957__topic_d46047e1_d46048e1_d46049e1_d46050e1_d46051e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217716e87\">\n                       \n Qualifiers\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Qualifiers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1__entry__1\">\n Qualifier\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/hex</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1__entry__2\">\n Returns a hexadecimal representation of the color in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/rgb</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1__entry__2\">\n Returns an RGB representation of the color in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/full</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6197e1_d6198e1_d6199e1__entry__2\">\n Starts a full size color box.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gix1665702628957__topic_d46052e1_d46053e1_d46054e1_d46055e1_d46056e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217716e163\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1__entry__3\">\n Values\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1__entry__4\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Color</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1__entry__3\">\n hex or RGB string\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6200e1_d6201e1_d6202e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Color to be highlighted when the Color dialog box is started.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Color</var> is not specified, the color box displays the\n                           last-selected color. Initially this is black. Selecting a color and\n                           clicking OK sets the last-selected color, which is used to initialize the\n                           colorbox for the next time it is used in the same application session.\n                           Closing the application deletes the last-selected color.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gix1665702628957__topic_d46057e1_d46058e1_d46059e1_d46060e1_d46061e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217716e236\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gix1665702628957__p_d70208e1_d70209e1_d70210e1\">The color returned by the dialog will be available in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6203e1_d6204e1_d6205e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6203e1_d6204e1_d6205e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6203e1_d6204e1_d6205e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6203e1_d6204e1_d6205e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6203e1_d6204e1_d6205e1__entry__2\"> The user ended the dialog by clicking\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">OK</span>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6203e1_d6204e1_d6205e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gix1665702628957__table_d6203e1_d6204e1_d6205e1__entry__2\"> The user ended the dialog by pressing <span class=\"ph keypress\">Esc</span> or by clicking the\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Cancel</span> or the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close</span>\n                        button.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gix1665702628957__topic_d46062e1_d46063e1_d46064e1_d46065e1_d46066e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217716e317\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gix1665702628957__d5909e20\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gix1665702628957__topic_d46067e1_d46068e1_d46069e1_d46070e1_d46071e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1217716e326\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gix1665702628957__p_d70220e1_d70221e1_d70222e1\">If the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Color</var> parameter is not defined, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">colorbox</span> uses the last selected color. Initially, this is black. Selecting a color and clicking OK initializes the last selected color internally. This is used to initialize the Color dialog when started again in the same application session. Closing the application deletes the last selected color.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gix1665702628957__p_d70223e1_d70224e1_d70225e1\">Without the <code class=\"ph codeph\">/full</code> switch, the an abbreviated version of the Color dialog box is displayed:</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"gix1665702628957__fig_d70226e1_d70227e1_d70228e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Color Dialog Box</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Basic color dialog window\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/colorbox.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gix1665702628957__p_d70232e1_d70233e1_d70234e1\">When started with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">/full</code> switch, the illustrated Color dialog box is started:</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"gix1665702628957__fig_d70235e1_d70236e1_d70237e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Full Color Dialog Box</figcaption>\n<br/><img alt=\"Detail color dialog window\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/colorboxfull.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">Start the Color dialog box with the specified green color highlighted,\n               and return the user's color selection as a hex number:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">colorbox /hex \"#00FF00\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Start the Color dialog box with the specified green color highlighted, and return the user's color selection as an RGB number:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">colorbox /rgb \"0,128,0\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Start the full Color dialog box with the specified green color highlighted, and return the user's color selection as a hex number:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">colorbox /hex /full \"#00FF00\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ncx1686824523526.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$result</a><p>Return the result of certain ProcScript commands and tree widget events.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4814677\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4814677\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "colorbox Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Start the Microsoft Windows Color dialog box. Explain this code colorbox {/hex | /rgb} {/full} {\"Color\"} Copy Example: colorbox /hex /full \"#00FF00\" Note: The colorbox widget supports accessibility feature only for testing purposes and screen readers only. For more information, see Accessibility . Qualifiers Table 1. Qualifiers Qualifier Description /hex Returns a hexadecimal representation of the color in $result . /rgb Returns an RGB representation of the color in $result . /full Starts a full size color box. Parameters Table 2. Parameters Parameter Data Type Values Description Color String hex or RGB string Color to be highlighted when the Color dialog box is started. If Color is not specified, the color box displays the last-selected color. Initially this is black. Selecting a color and clicking OK sets the last-selected color, which is used to initialize the colorbox for the next time it is used in the same application session. Closing the application deletes the last-selected color. Return Values The color returned by the dialog will be available in $result . Table 3. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 0 The user ended the dialog by clicking OK . <0 The user ended the dialog by pressing Esc or by clicking the Cancel or the Close button. Use Use in Form components. Description If the Color parameter is not defined, colorbox uses the last selected color. Initially, this is black. Selecting a color and clicking OK initializes the last selected color internally. This is used to initialize the Color dialog when started again in the same application session. Closing the application deletes the last selected color. Without the /full switch, the an abbreviated version of the Color dialog box is displayed: Figure 1. Color Dialog Box When started with the /full switch, the illustrated Color dialog box is started: Figure 2. Full Color Dialog Box Start the Color dialog box with the specified green color highlighted, and return the user's color selection as a hex number: colorbox /hex \"#00FF00\" Copy Start the Color dialog box with the specified green color highlighted, and return the user's color selection as an RGB number: colorbox /rgb \"0,128,0\" Copy Start the full Color dialog box with the specified green color highlighted, and return the user's color selection as a hex number: colorbox /hex /full \"#00FF00\" Copy Related Links $result Return the result of certain ProcScript commands and tree widget events. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}